íŸ@e26c4c30f1642e3b187a0518da01290945b05569e9d5c15fc3139c541177779b⁄,Title: title: attr example
Path: Examples
Content:
Add examples to custom command.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> # Double numbers
    @example "double an int" { 2 | double } --result 4
    @example "double a float" { 0.25 | double } --result 0.5
    def double []: [number -> number] { $in * 2 }


```
